org.apache.flink.graph.examples.data

类 IncrementalSSSPData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.graph.examples.data.IncrementalSSSPData

  • public class IncrementalSSSPData
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides the default data sets used for the IncrementalSSSP example program. If no parameters are given to the program, the default data sets are used.
